<br>
A quick response to &quot;make something else&quot; suggestion... I happen to <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> like</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> playing a druid. I've tried several other classes and think they're fun, but druids are by far my favorite. So there! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I'll just have to put up /role and nasty tells when I say no.<br>
<br>
